{"tid":1563300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[揀一首代表香港嘅歌]同舟之情 vs 願榮光歸香港","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:21:56.000Z","uid":12558,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0698494430e8615294d15ae620ee8cc7edfd42c4","tid":1563300,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"《同舟之情》（Sail On）為香港政府於2013年舉辦「家是香港」活動之主題曲，由郭偉亮作曲，陳詠謙填詞，<span style=\"color: red;\">張學友</span>及<span style=\"color: red;\">陳奕迅</span>合唱。當中歌曲中亦引用了顧嘉煇及黃霑的《獅子山下》歌曲中的部分主旋律及歌詞，從而帶出香港精神。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L3iul2AFq-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL3iul2AFq-Y&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=f72b3dfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L3iul2AFq-Y</a><br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港 只係一首唔知咩人作嘅網路歌曲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oUIDL4SB60g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoUIDL4SB60g&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=8576c48f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oUIDL4SB60g</a><br />\n<br />\n同舟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n榮光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cd0ecc847e1b26781148e13defb6a60fbbcda1","tid":1563300,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: cente